---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import ButtonWhite from '../components/ButtonWhite.astro';
import Link from '../components/Link.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import thumbsup from "../assets/images/thumbsup.png";
import ButtonBlack from "../components/ButtonBlack.astro";
---
<MainLayout title="Home">
<section class="relative isolate min-h-[120vh] md:min-h-[110vh]">
  <!-- Baggrundsbillede -->
  <img
    src="/hero.png"
    alt=""
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 w-full h-full object-cover object-bottom"
    aria-hidden="true"
  />

  <!-- Logo -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div></div>

    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <img 
        class="w-[70%] md:w-[68%] pt-25 mx-auto md:mx-0" 
        src="svg/logo_hero.svg" 
        alt="Instant Day Logo"
      >
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tekst -->
  <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 text-center mt-10">
    <p class="font-heading text-[24px] md:text-[28px] leading-tight text-[var(--color-beige)]">
      Join us the 18th of October
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA-knapper -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 pt-8 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <ButtonWhite>
      Submit a photo
    </ButtonWhite>

    <ButtonWhite >
      Save the date
    </ButtonWhite>

    <ButtonWhite>
      See the gallery
    </ButtonWhite>
  </div>
</section>
<!---------------------------------------------SLUT HERO HER-->


<section class="container-global py-12 md:py-20 px-10 sm:px-6">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-12 gap-y-10 md:gap-y-16">

    <!-- Række 1: What is InstantDay -->
    <div class="md:col-start-2 md:col-span-10">
      <h1>What is InstantDay?</h1>
      <h2 class="mt-2">A day for the love of nostalgia and photography</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-prose">
        October 18 is Instant Day - a day all about celebrating instant photography. So get out your Polaroid,
        Instax or whatever instant photography camera you are using, and show us your instants. Instant Day isn’t
        really a photo competition, it’s more a homage to good old analogue, instant photography - everybody who
        participates are winners. But: We do have a nice prize for one lucky instant photographer!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Række 2: Why instant photography (tekst) -->
    <div class="md:row-start-2 md:col-start-6 md:col-span-7 md:-mt-12">
      <h1>Why instant photography?</h1>
      <h2 class="mt-2">Instant Photography is a testament to life</h2>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 max-w-prose">
        <p>
      It all started back in the 1940’s with a 3 year old kid. She wanted to see her fathers images right away. The father, Edwin Land, embarked on a mission: To invent instant photography. Half a decade later, Edwin Land launched Instant photography and established the Polaroid brand. Instant photography turned into big business in the 70’s and 80’s, until the digital era almost killed the industry.
 
The massive amount of time wasted on the small screens have spurred a counterreaction: Analogue, off-line experiences have become popular again. And instant photography is just that: An analogue, life-affirming and tactile photography experience. So let’s celebrate life, and make memories!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- tegning: mobil = efter teksten, højrejusteret.
         Desktop = venstre for 2. sektion (kol. 2-4). -->
   <div
  class="order-3 flex justify-end mt-6
         md:order-none md:row-start-2 md:col-start-2 md:col-span-3 md:justify-start md:mt-0">
  <img 
    src="/svg/instax_drawing.svg" 
    alt="" 
    class="w-24 sm:w-28 md:w-40 lg:w-48"
  />
</div>
  </div>

  <!---------------------------------------------SLUT sektion 1 HER-->

</section>







</MainLayout>

